true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615198\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615198\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pjk1665702632381.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pjk1665702632381.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pjk1665702632381.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pjk1665702632381\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Tool Tip (\n                              ToolTip)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether a tool tip is displayed when the cursor hovers over the command button or an enabled polygon. It only applies if the field contains a glyph. <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> (default) or <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pjk1665702632381__p_d108263e1_d108264e1_d108265e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>ToolTip<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> |\n        <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pjk1665702632381__section_onn_43f_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d119874e74\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pjk1665702632381__table_d12758e1_d12759e1_d12760e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported in Grid?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">For command buttons, this property is supported only when\n                    <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Representation</span> is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface</code>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pjk1665702632381__section_hhs_p3f_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d119874e144\">Command Button</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pjk1665702632381__p_d108272e1_d108273e1_d108274e1\">If the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tool Tip Text</span> property\n        is specified, it takes precedence over <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tool Tip</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pjk1665702632381__p_d108275e1_d108276e1_d108277e1\">If the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Auto Label</span> property is\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, and there is an associated label, no tool tip is displayed, even if\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tool Tip</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pjk1665702632381__section_bqh_s3f_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d119874e174\">Map</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pjk1665702632381__p_d108281e1_d108282e1_d108283e1\">The tool tip text is defined as a text message with\n        the same name as the glyph. This message can be up to 1024 characters in length. If no\n        message exists, the polygon's tag title is used by default.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pjk1665702632381__section_e5c_t3f_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d119874e183\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pjk1665702632381__ul_ksg_53f_1xb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pjk1665702632381__li_d42299e1_d42300e1_d42301e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a>, including Uniface Button and Header Button </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pjk1665702632381__li_d42302e1_d42303e1_d42304e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gls1665702643795.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gls1665702643795.html\" title=\"The umap widget defines areas on an image that allow the user to interact by clicking on that area. It can only be used in form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called Map, which is mapped to umap.\">umap (Map)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gbk1665702628600.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Tool Tip Text (ToolTipText)</a><p>This property specifies the text to be displayed when the cursor is positioned over the widget. It can be a string up to 1024 bytes.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jls1665702632169.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Auto Label (AutoLabel)</a><p>This property determines whether the label text for the command button is automatically updated when a new glyph is loaded. True (default) or False</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/btj1665702631955.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Representation</a><p>This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615198\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615198\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Tool Tip ( ToolTip) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Tool Tip ( ToolTip) Determines whether a tool tip is displayed when the cursor hovers over the command button or an enabled polygon. It only applies if the field contains a glyph. True (default) or False . \" ToolTip = True | False \" Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: For command buttons, this property is supported only when Representation is set to Uniface . Command Button If the Tool Tip Text property is specified, it takes precedence over Tool Tip . If the Auto Label property is True , and there is an associated label, no tool tip is displayed, even if Tool Tip is True . Map The tool tip text is defined as a text message with the same name as the glyph. This message can be up to 1024 characters in length. If no message exists, the polygon's tag title is used by default. Applies To CommandButton , including Uniface Button and Header Button umap (Map) Related Links Tool Tip Text (ToolTipText) This property specifies the text to be displayed when the cursor is positioned over the widget. It can be a string up to 1024 bytes. Auto Label (AutoLabel) This property determines whether the label text for the command button is automatically updated when a new glyph is loaded. True (default) or False Representation This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}